labels.submitBossData: Submit boss HP data to BPTimer

descriptions.submitBossData: When enabled, boss HP thresholds are automatically submitted to the BPTimer database to help the community track spawn times.
descriptions.clearOnServerChange: Automatically clears DPS statistics when changing servers or zones.
descriptions.clearOnTimeout: Automatically clears DPS statistics after a period of combat inactivity.
descriptions.disableTransparency: Disables transparent window background to reduce GPU load. Requires application restart to take effect. Recommended for best performance.
descriptions.transparencyAmount: Adjust the transparency level of the window background. 0% = fully transparent, 100% = fully opaque.
descriptions.lockPosition: Prevents all windows from being moved. Can also be toggled using the lock button on the main window.
descriptions.lockKeybind: Click the input field and press your desired key combination. Works globally even when the app is not focused.
descriptions.monstersKeybind: Toggle the Monsters window. Press the keybind to open or close the window.
descriptions.groupKeybind: Toggle the Group window. Press the keybind to open or close the window.
descriptions.settingsKeybind: Toggle the Settings window. Press the keybind to open or close the window.
descriptions.deviceKeybind: Toggle the Device window. Press the keybind to open or close the window.
descriptions.historyKeybind: Toggle the History window. Press the keybind to open or close the window.
descriptions.clickthrough: Enable permanent clickthrough mode. You won't be able to interact with the window until disabled. Use the lock button to toggle temporarily.
descriptions.enableManualHeight: When enabled, use the height adjustment buttons to manually control window height. When disabled, the window height automatically adjusts to fit content.
descriptions.heightAdjustmentStep: How many pixels the window height increases or decreases when using the height adjustment buttons. Only active when manual height adjustment is enabled. Default: 20px
descriptions.performanceMode: Reduces update frequency to 250ms (from 100ms) to improve FPS. Recommended if experiencing frame drops.
descriptions.updateInterval: How often the DPS meter updates. Higher values = better performance but less responsive. Default: 100ms
descriptions.checkForUpdates: Check if a new version of BPSR Meter is available on GitHub. Updates are automatically checked on startup.

update.reinstallWarning: You are already on the latest version. You can reinstall it if you're experiencing issues.
